Abdullah Almarzouq!

I’m a second year medical students at the Imam Abdulrahman Bin Faisal University and a member in MedSTEMPowered. MedSTEMPowered is an international Nonprofit Organization dedicated to building a community for Future M.D.s+ in STEM. I’m also passion about popularising science to general public. When I’m not studying, I love listening to music and play guitar.
